  "body": "From the docs of the Crowdsale:\r\nhttps://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-solidity/blob/14a59b29035ab8c9fdfb969550fe35f65e88d529/contracts/crowdsale/Crowdsale.sol#L48-L52\r\n\r\nBut then later:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-solidity/blob/14a59b29035ab8c9fdfb969550fe35f65e88d529/contracts/crowdsale/Crowdsale.sol#L119\r\n\r\nAnd finally:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-solidity/blob/14a59b29035ab8c9fdfb969550fe35f65e88d529/contracts/crowdsale/Crowdsale.sol#L191-L193\r\n\r\nThere is no check of the decimals of the token to be found. I came accross this because I could not get it to work to get 100 Tokens per Ether. I guess a test for the crowdsale with less decimals than 18 should be added.",
